## Most Google Ads Campaigns Are Set Up to Get Clicks, Not Customers

You've built a solid practice through referrals and word-of-mouth. When someone recommends you, they show up ready to book. But here's the problem: you can't control the flow. Some months are packed. Others are slow. You're at the mercy of your network instead of driving your own growth.

That's where Google Ads comes in — done right.

## How We Do It Differently

Every campaign is built around one goal: **turning searchers into patients who show up and pay.** Not clicks. Not leads. Patients.

We start by understanding your practice economics: your average patient value, your capacity, your margins, and your conversion bottlenecks. Then we build campaigns around those realities — not around vanity metrics.

## Real Results

One dermatology practice brought their cost-per-lead down to **$37** — 70% below the industry average of $120+ — by rebuilding their Google Ads strategy around operational reality. Read the full case study: [$37 Per Dermatology Lead](/blog/dermatology-lead-cost-case-study).

## What's Included

- Full campaign build and conversion tracking setup
- Keyword research grounded in your actual patient journey
- Ad copy written for healthcare audiences
- Landing page conversion review
- Ongoing optimization and reporting
- Direct founder access — no account manager layer

